content: And then the second part of that question is, for locations that have come back, what are we seeing in terms of depressed or less volumes than before, we're actually not seeing that, for most part they have crossed the pre pandemic levels, but it may not be because people have come back five days to work in the office, but it's more because the ticket sizes -- prices have gone up and they are just maybe buying more premium products and the product mix has shifted.
